text: Arisney Ramos (born 11 May 1989) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * china 19 cuba 6 fina * arisney-ramos-betancourt * cubas-arisney-ramos-betancourt-cubas-mayelin- bernal-villa * cubas-arisney-ramos-betancourt Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
